name: Hidden Object Crosswords
description: Try a whole new twist to Hidden Object games when you search for clues to complete Crossword puzzles. Simply click on the crossword puzzle to get a riddle hint, then try to figure out the item. How fast can you complete the puzzle to earn rewarding trophies? Search for clues and find the answers in more than 50 challenging levels. Fill in the blank to pop culture references, figure out proverbs, and decipher clever riddles. If you get stuck, click on the firefly for a letter hint, or click on the Hint button to reveal the item. With a relaxing pace, a soothing soundtrack, and wonderful riddles to solve, this unique game combination will surely keep you engaged.

name: Youda Fisherman
description: Prove Youda Fisherman praised in books and maintain your universal fame by helping a stranger rebuild his fishing company! Help the stranger face the fears you have once battled and unite with him in your next quest for fame. Use his extraordinary inventions and rule the seas in this electrifying journey and time management game!

name: Dust and Salt: Battle for Murk Gamebook
Drop by Hippo Cooperation
description:
Drop is a physics based puzzle game in which everything *DROPS* if you hover over it with your mouse.

Basically you just have to get the orange balls into the levels goal,but it gets a lot more complicated than that, introducing teleporters, barriers, lava blocks & much more!

name: Quick! Mom's Home!
description:
Do your chores, build your empire and don't get grounded! 
 
Your mom is pulling into the driveway! Hurry! Get your chores done before you get yourself grounded! 
Quick! Mom's Home! (QMH) is a simulation tycoon game. 
 
Demo your chores today!

name: Big Hunt: Paint Town Black Red
Mia and me: Freedom for Centopia
Jump, Smash!
description:
While it might sound simple, "Jump, Smash!" is a a test of speed, focus and control.
Easy to learn but hard to master, it's also crazy fun...and a bit addictive.

name: Be the King: Enjoy Your Trip to the Top
Owls - A matching game for kids.
Beyond the Legend: Mysteries of Olympus
description: Journey to ancient Greece to relieve a beautiful tale of romance in this exciting Hidden Object Adventure. Theron, a modest hunter deeply in love with the goddess Artemis, has to overcome all obstacles standing in their way to happiness. Travel with Theron across the worlds of mighty gods to finally reach Mount Olympus and to prove that he deserves to be with the goddess. Explore gorgeous locations and watch as this amazing and breathtaking story unfolds!

name: Castle Creeps TD
description:
Bring out your everyday Hero and lead troops to victory in the best fantasy mobile Tower Defense game! Fortify your defenses and prepare to save the kingdom from ferocious Warlords, colossal Ogres & savage Goblins! Change strategy on the fly in this challenging, non-stop action experience!
Face countless challenging battles & taste hard earned victory as you build, upgrade and repair horde-splatting Towers. Recruit and level up mighty Heroes to protect the kingdoms in this top Tower Defense experience!
Invite friends through Facebook and share magical powers to aid you in battle and defend the realm!

name: Truth or Dare? Fun Party Games
Planet Builder - Create Your Own Solar System
Frog Blast: Tap Cube to Blast
Memopoly
description:
It’s time to use your memory ability to find a way to solve the puzzle.
The rule is easy, just tap on the colors of the right-side 3D object and focus on the place of that color in the left-side pattern. You will need your concentration and memory to recognize the right place of each color. Then you should tap the colors one by one respectively and quickly.
Actually, It’s you that create the 3D object step by step by solving each pattern.

name: Hip Hop Battle - Girls vs. Boys Dance Clash
Dare! Truth or Dare Would You?
Nightmara
description: Old school horror with new school technology.

name: We Happy Few: Uncle Jack Live VR
description:
We Happy Few: Uncle Jack Live VR is your chance to meet and work with Wellington Wells’ most prominent celebrity figure. Help Uncle Jack produce an exceptional show by delivering only the happiest of news and ensuring Wellies everywhere remember to take their Joy.
You’ll not only deal with a very opinionated Uncle Jack, but also contend with a Downer Outbreak that has made its way into the broadcast studio. Using the tools at your disposal, you can not only survive the outbreak but hopefully quell the conflict itself.
When you’re done playing producer, spend some downtime in the media archives where you can explore over 40 Uncle Jack episodes, listen to official We Happy Few soundtrack selections, and watch bonus materials like trailers and animation reels.

name: Ragdoll Boxing: Match of the Century
Sprint Daytona Duel for Nascar HD
Nun
description: NUN is a third-person narrative and cinematic open-world adventure game, with action and RPG elements and a 1970s horror aesthetic. In 1820, Sister Mary-Martin, a Templar agent, is sent on a mission to the land of Winchester to investigate the mysterious disappearance of a young nun.

name: Heaven's Point
description:
In a city plagued with crime and corruption, one man fights to save both the soul of the city as well as his own. 
 
In the year 199X, the streets of Heaven's Point is but a thin web hiding a dark hive of violent gangs, manipulative corporations and corrupt politicians. 
 
The decent people of the city live in fear as any soul brave enough to stand up to these criminals quickly disappears into the shadows never to be seen again. 
 
When his dearest friend falls prey to the scum of the Devil Dogs one man must draw strength from the violent past he had hoped never would surface again. 
 
It's time to tear the heart of the city from the jaws of darkness and bring it back to the light.

name: RGB
description: Enjoy a relaxing game with 3 colors and a lot of skill, your only task is to make the different color balls fall into their matching color using your mouse

name: Tap Duels Tournament
description:
Duel friends and players from all across the world. Engage in a realtime PVP experience based on tactics and skill in this soon-to-be-released game on iOS and Android. 
 
Wield different weapons and build your strategy around your playstyle to become the ultimate tournament champion.

name: Kanji Game - Learn and Practice Japanese
Would You Rather? For Battle Royale
Zodiac Battles
description:
Choose your zodiac sign, control the element according to your sign and enter the online arena to battle! 
 
Battle other players in an epic all out war against the other signs! Play on a unique world, each having a special ability and home to one of the signs! 
 
Apart from standard modes such as Free for all. Play one of the unique modes such as battle of the 4, where 4 players will fight to the death, each player representing the element of their sign! Player with the highest kills wins!

name: Lola's Fruity Sudoku
description: Lola’s Fruity Sudoku is specially designed for kids ages 4 to 8. Attractive animated instructions help children get into the game easily and they can quickly learn to play even without knowing what Sudoku is.

name: Space Run : Super Car Endless Game 2014
Shark Puzzles for Kids Jigsaw Wonder Collection
Fuzzy Seasons: Animal Forest (Start Pack Edition)
The epic of legend 1 -The Tower of Lost
MoBu - Adventure Begins
description:
Meet MoBu, the laziest ape in the jungle, who has the appetite of 5 elephants. One day MoBu meets a whimsical voodoo magician MaGu, who lends MoBu a supernatural power that allows him to infinitely extend his arms. However, if MoBu wants to satisfy his hunger now, he has to eat bananas... A lot of bananas.
MoBu is an action-packed simple platformer game with fun mechanics designed for mobile devices. Instead of running or flying, MoBu swings his arms to victory against his hunger.
Maneuver through uniquely designed environments like vile jungles and toxic dumps. The innovative game mechanics, combined with beautiful and humorous art style, will give you a memorable and funny game experience.

name: 4-in-1 Version 9
description: 4 -in 1 Volume 9 was the ninth volume of 4-in-1 multicarts made by Sachen. It contains: Zipball, Small Gorilla, Crazy Burger, and Deep: Final Mission.

name: Alive
description: Welcome to Alive , a Third person Cover based shooter. Bring in your friends and join the battle to become the best player, you will get the opportunity to pull off your skills and make your way to the top of the Leader board by earning XPs!

name: Word Tropics - Free Word Games and Puzzles
Fat[EX] Courier Simulator
description: In the game FatEx Curier Simulator you play as a courier for special tasks. You will have to deliver many parcels, despite all adversities.

name: Hentai Sokoban
description: By solving puzzles you reward yourself with the girls pictures & Steam achievements.

name: Myths of the World: Of Fiends and Fairies HD
Virtual Earth Online
description:
Imagine a game like Minecraft but multiplayer and the size of Earth. Virtual Earth Online uses Google Earth technology to recreate the entire Earth within the game. Your house is in this game! Every river, road, tree is here. Build cities and teleport around the world to your friend’s creations. We have a huge variety of materials that enable you to create anything you want to create. 
Virtual Earth Online is multiplayer over the internet. Use blocks and other building materials to build houses, farms or cities.

name: Bleak
description: Bleak is a Sci-Fi survival game. You must fight the planetary environments to survive and thrive. You can build bases, mine resources, research new technology and discover new flora and fauna. Play alone or coop with friends, its up to you.

name: Slam Dunk - The best basketball game 2018
Dabwoman: When the Dab isn't Sexist
description: What is Dabwoman? Do I really need to explain this? I guess so, because I need a description. Well, Dabwoman is the best super hero video game ever made, want to argue on that? Alright, we are going to meet behind the school in 2 hours. You want to know the story? Alright, well it's a woman, and she eats a laundry pod for no reason what so ever, and guess what? She becomes a super hero, you gotta admit that's pretty dope. I'm not going to tell you the whole story, so just play the game man. It's like a movie, but interactive, go make some popcorn and play it, if you don't play it.. then you are a bully. Being a bully is bad.

name: A Good Librarian Like a Good Shepherd
Banana girl
description: Bananas girl, is a RPG fun game. It tells the heroine, born and grown from the village, around the bananas, and has a series of interesting stories.

name: Airline Commander: A Real Flight Experience
High School: Bisexual Experience
description: This story also relates to the typical life of an openly bisexual girl in highschool who suffers many hardships everyday, just trying to maintain her self-image at a stable point and living life the best way she can- even with the reputation as "dyke".

name: Hentai University
description: Plunge in the world of knowledge from another universe, which you will visit as a student and where you will learn new subjects. You will be met by excellent teachers who will need to be conquered. The game is based on the Match3 mechanics, and all this is presented in the shape of visual novels

name: Rat Arena
description: Rat Arena is the battle of Humans and Artificial Intelligence. Try to defeat my ai-rat in this battle in the arena! Prove that people can be as good as machines!

name: In the Village of Grandfather: Summer,Sun,Heat.
description: Roast, sunny, my summer. I came to help my grandfather. Build my farm and find love.

name: Snake Bricks-Bounce Balls
description:
Swipe left and right, manipulate the baffle, bounce a snake consisting of small balls, and constantly bounce and hit the bricks!
As the bricks fall, try to adjust the angle, collect more balls, let the snake grow longer and break all the bricks!

name: Fallen Emiya
description: This game talks about a story of the Brave Emiya who destoried the Dark Lord. But after that Emiya cursed, and became a mixed devil. At the same time, she chased by human beings who didn't knew the truth. So Emiya was determined to find a way to lift the curse. The player's choice will decide the ending of Emiya.

name: Mayonez
description: A dark comedy adventure RPG, set in the fictional Slavic industrial town of Mayonez.

name: Live or Die: Survival
description: Live or Die: Zombie Apocalypse Survival plunges you into a post-apocalyptic world overrun by the undead. Combining the best of RPG, survival, shooting, and action genres, this open-world adventure challenges you to survive against all odds. Explore a desolate landscape, gather essential resources, craft and upgrade your equipment, and build an impenetrable base. Complete challenging quests, battle hordes of zombies and powerful mutants, and even build your own motorcycle to traverse the ravaged world. Inspired by survival classics, Live or Die tests your skills and your will to live.

name: QB Sim
description: Advanced Quarterback Simulator in VR. Design and create plays in seconds. Suitable for professional teams through to anyone who wants to experience the complexities and nuances of QB play. Configurable and includes 18 years of NFL game statistics.

name: Miner Ultra Wild Tides
description: In this new adventure, Miner and his friends will have to be the greatest of the seven seas to face creatures and lovecraftian places, to become increasingly powerful so they can navigate the world of H.P. Lovecraft !!! A 2d platform game with rogue-like elements and physically real water !!!

name: The Psychic
description: Be a Psychic to experience a larruping adventure. Living in the foggy place and exploring the unknown. Collecting resources and discovering magic treasures. Build and expand your own castle.

name: Homespace
description:
Welcome to Homespace! Transform your charming fixer upper into a one-of-a-kind home made just for you, designed by you! Take rooms from drab to fab by playing puzzles to earn unique furniture and decor. 
 
Beat challenging puzzle levels to fix and furnish rooms in your new house. Are you up to the task? Home is where your story begins

name: Cobi Darts
description:
Have great fun and play with all your friends as you perfect your aim and try to win.
With awesome multiplayer modes and amazing single player modes, Cobi Darts lets you play with all your friends, or just throw some darts for fun to sharpen up your game.

name: Boom Brothers
description:
Boom Brothers is a team based multiplayer third person shooter with vehicular combat. Customise your soldier's look and talk with teammates and enemies through text to speech chat!

Fly fighter and bomber planes, drive tanks and jeeps and fight alongside your friends in Boom Brothers.

name: Contingent
description: An action RPG set in late Roman Britannia, Contingent focuses on gritty skill based combat combined with mass AI warfare. Lay siege to fortifications, capture settlements and villages, and pillage supply lines in intense strategical combat.

name: Fugue State
description: Explore a haunted dreamscape, inspired by the likes of Yume Nikki, Strawberry cubes, and other avant garde "walking simulators." Something dark lies behind The Wanderer's dreams, locked in Fugue State. 11 items hold the clues, but must first be found. You have eternity. Good luck.

name: Bitter Tides
description: Set in a mysterious desert dream world, Bitter Tides is a first-person stealth and horror game. Your tools are lures and traps with which you avoid and ensnare those creeping things from the deep.

name: Deep Rest
description: Deep Rest is a psychological adventure horror game. With a deep focus on storytelling both direct, indirect & on unique features. Utilizing a point and click interact system. Combining aspects of different genres & innovative mechanics, such as time travel, drawing sigils & paranormal events. You shape the story, you have the ability to make dramatic changes.

name: Vixens From outer Space
description: -A Single Player First Person Shooter History- Space Amazons! Cosmic Horror! Action! And dangerous curves!

name: Mukti
description: Mukti is a first person story exploration game setup in an Indian Museum that revolves around one of the hard hitting social issue globally, human trafficking!

name: Cookie Baker
description:
Get in your very own kitchen, it's time to bake some cookies!
Mix many kinds of ingredients and bake according to the chef's recommended recipe book.

name: Word Club: Word Puzzle Game
description:
Play with friends or other word nerds from all over the world! Whomp your opponents by getting the longest words and the top score! Have fun while you train your brain!
It’s easy to play but takes time to master because of the multitude of bonuses and win strategies.
Try out best word game for some good instant fun as a word search. Whether you’re a beginner at word games or a word scramble master, it’s a smart and exciting experience!

name: My Kingdom for the Princess IV HD
War.io : Zombie Battle Royale
description: War.io : Zombie Battle Royale - this is a huge fight in the deathmatch mode. Modifying the 2d top-down shooter takes you to a world where you have to fight for your own life.

name: Arkanoid For Painters
description: You in the game Arkanoid for Painters will have to help them destroy them. To do this you need to use the ball floating in the water.

name: 4-in-1 Version 4
description: 4 -in 1 Volume 4 was the fourth volume of 4-in-1 multicarts made by Sachen. It contains: Pile Wonder, Snake Roy, Suleiman's Treasure, and Puppet Knight.

name: 4-in-1 Version 3
description: 4 -in 1 Volume 3, also known as Commin 4-in-1, was the third volume of 4-in-1 multicarts made by Sachen. It contains: Taiwan's Mahjong, Japan's Mahjong, Hong Kong's Mahjung, and Store Tris 2.

name: 4-in-1 Version 2
description: 4 -in 1 Volume 2 was the second volume of 4-in-1 multicarts made by Sachen. It contains: Virus Attack, Electron World, Dice Square, and Trouble Zone.

name: 4-in-1 Version 1
description: 4 -in 1 Volume 1 was the first volume of 4-in-1 multicarts made by Sachen. It contains: Street Rider, Vex Block, Trap & Turn, and Duck Adventures.

name: Yet Another Exhausting Day
description: You are exhausted, but why not go to sleep? A 3D crawling platformer about ordinary people’s exhausted life. Play as an exhausted person, and do everything you can to fight the drowsiness.

name: Crush the Numbers
description:
Welcome to Crush the Numbers! 
 
In Crush the Numbers, you solve brain game problems by writing the answers as fast as you can. 
 
This game uses daily exercises designed to promote brain wellness. 
 
Keep your brain sharp in the following areas: 
● Concentration 
● Focus 
● Math 
● Memory 
● Cognitive skills 
● Working memory 
● Computations 
● Puzzle/Problem-solving 
● Brainpower 
 
Play games and level up in life.

name: Tales of Kid Goblin: Puzzle Crush!
Westward 2
description: Stake your claim today! Fortune is yours for the taking! Steer the fortunes of three adventurous pioneers as they build and defend their ever-growing settlement from dangerous bandits determined to cheat or steal from anyone they cross.

name: The Mystery of the Crimson Manor
RiceCakers
description: RiceCakers is an easy and funny fight game, customizing the appearance of your Rice Caker Monster, and fights with the enemies in the different scenes for a moment, or with a good friend in the LAN.

name: Midnight Pulse
description: In this stylish rhythm platformer you will traverse an obstacle ridden terrain while listening to a wide variety of music. Listen carefully because you must base your movements off the music to successfully complete each level. Equiped with a fully functional level editor create levels with your own music and share them with your friends!

name: Camping with girls
description: "Camping with girls" is a short Visual Novel created by BCH Waves studio. The story seems to be very interesting with some sexy details...

name: Sweet Girl Adventure 2
description:
Sweet Girl Adventure is a little adventure game with a beautiful graphic style 
 This is a second part of adventure. Don't forget to check out the second part! 
 You play as a little girl who wants to collect as much candies as possible for a limited time.

name: WarBox: Camouflage
description: WarBox: Camouflage combines all the great features of modern hero shooters, mixes in a lot of characters, and add a ton of environmental interaction to create an over-the-top, fun experience.

name: Survival on Raft in the Ocean
Car Showroom: Luxury Sports Auto Racing Simulator
Kingdoms of the Dump
description:
Kingdoms of the Dump is a SNES-style RPG with platforming elements and turn-based combat developed by the New Jersey-based Roach Games.

Join the trashcan knight, Dustin Binsley, as he fights his way through the Five and Half Kingdoms of the Dump. Rescue the trashpicked King, defeat the totally disgusting Toxic Grimelin Army and prevent the Lands of Fill from an all-out war!

name: Forgive Me My Henchmen
description: A tower defence game where you get to play as the 'bad guy' - Deploy henchmen and sabotage a building to delay a one-man army action hero.

name: In Space We Brawl: Full Arsenal Edition
Touchdowners
description:
Touchdowners is a crazy physics based sports game where you need to grab the ball and touch it down in your opponents endzone!
You control a team of three highly trained Touchdowners. Pass, wrestle and jump your way to the end zone then slam the ball to the ground.

name: Stretch!
description: Drive the bus from tower to tower!

name: Steer Clear
description: Steer Clear is a game about navigating a tugboat and barge through narrow ports, and increasingly complex waters. Along the way players can drop off deliveries at docks for gold! The waters and environment are procedurally generated to create a brand-new experience each time played!

name: Bubble Shooter: Classic Pop
description: Rethink the bubble shooter genre and blast your way to victory with Bouncing Bubbles! Download this endlessly entertaining arcade shooter, start shooting away at rows of bubbles, and discover exactly how addicting bouncing bubbles level in and level out can be!

name: Solitaire Whizz
description: The ultimate comprehensive, great value solitaire collection for your iPad: 40 addictive solitaire/patience card games in one a single app! No hidden extra purchases! For ONE single purchase, get ALL games, including Free Cell (Windows solitaire), Klondike (classic solitaire), Pyramid 13, Poker Solitaire, Yukon, Spider, Golf, Russian Solitaire and a host of other games! All with high-quality retina graphics, turn tips, auto-complete, scrolling/zooming, sound effects/animation...

name: Pick and Learn - Easy Learning for Kids
Domination Earth
description:
Android and iOS AR strategy game “Domination: Earth" operates in the real world around you - military style! Check in wherever you go using your phone or tablet to capture places and pieces of land, expanding your very own global empire - like Geocaching on Steroids!  
 
A health conscious and adventure provoking platform, it encourages hiking, cycling and other forms of travel and real-world exploration in order to collect resources - you have to physically approach each item wherever it appears in the world to pick it up. 
 
Game tactics include capturing lands to build military bases and recruiting armies to establish regional dominance. Construction resources keep appearing all over the globe, so in the process of their collection you will explore places you've never seen before! 
 
To defend your territories, initiate alliances with neighbors to fight against foreign threats or build a missile launcher in your backyard to thwart invaders of your hometown. It’s vital check in five times in any spot to establish a new base of operations. Once you've collected enough resources you can send your armies to the overseas base in order to advance your influence remotely, even after you've left! 
 
Domination Earth also engages in "item scrapping": any real-world item with a barcode can be transformed into a resource by using your camera (don't worry, you still get to keep your items afterwards!). Books, toys, DVDs - almost anything becomes a source of crafting materials.

name: Night Racing: Miami Street Traffic Racer
Dancing Ballz: Magic Dance Line Tiles Game
Happy Empire 2: The Lost Relic
description: Find mysterious relics inside an ancient chamber and progress through the Empire by using the power of those relics. Unite the Empire! Defeat the Evil Wizard and return home victorious!
